## Skill routing

1. No `docs/vibage/STATUS.md` → **vibage-init**
2. Hub ready, no qualified map (unless owner said MAP_SKIP) → **vibage-pile-index**
3. Map ready, no valid CONFIRM (= owner OK on the scan plan) → **vibage-orient**
4. CONFIRM OK → **vibage-issue-locate** (legacy install name `vibage-locate` OK)
5. NEW-CHAT / install unclear → **vibage-bootstrap** or **vibage-init** (then using-vibage)
6. Optional (not required for locate DONE): **vibage-issue-fix**, **vibage-arch-review**

Read package `STATUS.md` first (capability SSOT) before expanding scope.
After locate DONE → finishing options in **using-vibage** (required).

Host-best note: project `.cursor/hooks.json` sessionStart may inject context; if the host drops it, this **alwaysApply** rule still routes. See `references/host-best-session-entry.md`.

